Dr. Jekyll is a [[random event]] in which Dr. Jekyll appears and urgently asks the player for help. If talked to, he requests a clean [[Herb|herb]] of the player. If the player has a herb in their inventory, he will take it and give them a [[potion]], but if the player has no herbs he will give the player a [[Strength potion]] (2) before disappearing, saying he isn't safe with it. He will not accept noted herbs.

